```plantuml
@startuml gaiax_fLibra

actor User
participant "Nuxt.js Frontend" as Frontend
participant "Libra Blockchain" as Libra
participant "Ethereum Smart Contract" as Ethereum
participant "Firestore" as Firestore
participant "Elasticsearch Node.js" as Elasticsearch

User -> Frontend: Access marketplace
Frontend -> Firestore: Retrieve user profile
Firestore -> Frontend: User profile data

User -> Frontend: Search for items
Frontend -> Elasticsearch: Search by keyword/category
Elasticsearch -> Frontend: Search results

User -> Frontend: Select item to purchase
Frontend -> Libra: Initiate coin transfer
Libra -> Frontend: Confirm transfer

Frontend -> Ethereum: Execute smart contract
Ethereum -> Frontend: Confirm contract execution

User -> Frontend: Post item for sale
Frontend -> Firestore: Store item details
Firestore -> Elasticsearch: Index item data

User -> Frontend: Leave review
Frontend -> Firestore: Store review data
Firestore -> Ethereum: Update smart contract

@enduml
```